# --- ABOUT ---
msgid "About Hungary"
msgstr "Magyarországról"

msgid "Hungary has a rich history and vibrant culture."
msgstr "Magyarország gazdag történelemmel és élénk kultúrával rendelkezik."

msgid "Hungary has a long and complex history, influenced by various cultures and empires. It has been home to the Magyars since the 9th century and has seen periods of Ottoman, Habsburg, and Soviet influence."
msgstr "Magyarország hosszú és összetett történelemmel rendelkezik."

msgid "Learn more in our History section."
msgstr "További információ a Történelem oldalon."

msgid "Language"
msgstr "Nyelv"

msgid "Hungarian (Magyar) is the official language of Hungary. It is a unique language belonging to the Uralic language family and is not closely related to other European languages."
msgstr "A magyar hivatalos nyelv."

msgid "Want to learn more? Check out our Language page."
msgstr "Szeretne többet megtudni? Nézze meg a Nyelv oldalt."

msgid "Cultural Identity"
msgstr "Kulturális identitás"

msgid "Hungarians take great pride in their cultural heritage, which includes traditional music, dance, cuisine, and festivals. The country is known for its vibrant folk traditions and contributions to art and literature."
msgstr "A magyarok büszkék kulturális örökségükre."

msgid "Explore Culture & Traditions and view our Gallery."
msgstr "Fedezze fel a Kultúra és hagyományok oldalt."

msgid "Cuisine & Traditions"
msgstr "Konyha és hagyományok"

msgid "Discover traditional Hungarian dishes in our Food section and learn about celebrations in Holidays. Explore iconic Landmarks as well."
msgstr "Fedezze fel a hagyományos magyar ételeket és ünnepeket."

